    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of tree, reaching 24 m (80 feet) in height. It is found in estuarine ecosystems throughout the tropics, growing on aerial prop roots that arch above the water level.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
